Description:
Brand new waterfront home available. Discounted for nomination sale!
On Offer is this fabulous apartment located on the 26th floor in the newly completed 889 Collins Street residential complex.
Comprising of two bedrooms, two bathrooms and one car space, this brand new unit is located right on the promenade which showcases the great water aspect the Yarra River offers.
The unit incorporates a stylish kitchen with a separate bench and stainless steel appliances. Ideal for the budding chef as this provides ample preparation space and storage.
The main bedroom consists of an ensuite and walk through robe, whilst the second bedroom has a built in robe and direct access to the balcony.
Additional features include:
• Floor boards in the kitchen, dining and living area
• Carpeted bedrooms
• Air conditioning
• Covered balcony
• Car park on title
• High quality fixture and fittings
Residential Complex Features include:
• Indoor pool, gym and lounge
• Rooftop terrace with landscaped gardens, outdoor dining and BBQ
Great central precinct to reside in being set in the heart of the Docklands.
Cafes, restaurants, eateries, and other shops are right at your doorstep.
Woolworths located nearby along with the Library at the Dock.
The free Tram zone is a plus and the bike tracks offers plenty for riders.
As this is a nomination sale for this brand new unit yet to settlement, there is potential maximum stamp duty savings! Don't delay, call Peter Doan on 0423 399 999 for more information.

Description:
Absolute Waterfront and Unsurpassed Views
Convesso building has set the benchmark for luxury living within the Docklands precinct. The view from this luxury waterfront apartment is spectacular with uninterrupted view across the water to NewQuay and beyond, the marina below or down the river to the Bolte bridge.
- North aspect apartment which is light filled and great floor plan
- New public library at your doorstep and Woolworth supermarket in the precinct
- One minute walk to the nearest tram stop
- Resort style facilities with 24 hour concierge, residents lounge, business centre and board room, Cinema (within Concavo building), North facing Sky Garden facing the water with BBQ, 25 metre pool, spa, sauna, gym and treatment room
- Two spacious bedrooms with a wide balcony perfectly for entertaining/relaxing, stone benhtops in the kitchen, European kitchen appliances, ducted air conditioning and heating, separate laundry room, one secure undercover car space and storage cage.

Description:
Premier Water Views From Designer Docklands Abode
Experience the dynamism of Docklands from the sheer comfort of this light-filled 18th-floor apartment within The Palladio – a luxurious tower in the desirable New Quay precinct.
Filled with views across Victoria Harbour and beyond, the full-width balcony flows inside to a stunning open-plan living, dining and stone kitchen boasting stainless steel splashback and appliances.
Appreciate the 3 balconies and relaxing view from the two double bedrooms with built-in robes, accompanied by sparkling stone bathrooms and separate laundry.
Stay in to enjoy the premium onsite facilities including a pool with views, gym, residents’ lounge and gardens. Alternatively, head out to the many acclaimed restaurants, outstanding entertainment options including Harbour Town shopping, Etihad Stadium and quick access to the CBD via the tram.
A high-performing investment for your portfolio or an exciting new home.

Description:
Breathtaking Space in Stunning Arkley Living
Graced with wonderful contemporary elegance and an extraordinary amount of internal space (approx. 130sqm) that makes everyday living a genuine joy, this brilliant three bedroom, two bathroom residence is one of the true highlights of the coveted Arkley complex.
With the convenience of a first floor location, this spacious apartment is truly a delight to experience. The expansive lounge and dining zone has more space than you’ll know what to do with. The commanding kitchen perfectly is placed to look out over the central living zone. The kitchen further boasts sleek granite benchtops and quality stainless steel appliances.
The generous balcony has touches of tranquil greenery and views down to the promenade below, the space is ideal for summer meals or entertaining friends and family. The master bedroom fits in with the rest of the apartment in enjoying fabulous space while further boasting a walk-in robe and stylish ensuite. The other bedrooms deliver built-in robes and are just steps to the main bathroom which has a separate toilet in the power room and collecting separate laundry room.
Other enticing residence features include wall heating, air conditioning, secure intercom and storage cage plus 2 secure car spaces on the same level as the apartment. You’ll also have access to a swimming pool, spa, golf practice net and gym.
This exciting NewQuay Precinct has become one of the more popular Docklands areas to live, thanks to its location close to sensational waterside restaurants including Docklands Pizzeria, Oscars Table and Renzo’s Bar Café Italiano, as well as Harbour Town Shopping Centre, IGA and Asian supermarkets, Etihad Stadium and trams taking you all over Melbourne.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Call this Home – 128SQM of Waterfront Luxury
Stunning on all fronts thanks to its stylish sophistication, outstanding CBD and Port Phillip Bay vistas and relaxed open space on the 24th floor, this 2 bedroom + study, 2 bathroom corner apartment is a special offering in one of the Dockland’s best buildings.
The brilliant waterside location in the award winning Yarra Point oozes quality throughout. The apartment offers panoramic bay and CBD views from the living spaces, CBD and river views from the main bedroom, whilst the study/guest bedroom and second bedroom have magnificent bayside views.
The stone-featured kitchen includes a handy island bench, abundance of storage and stainless steel Miele appliances. The master bedroom delivers a stylish double vanity ensuite with built-in robe and access to private balcony. Take advantage of the large main balcony with superb views, 2nd bedroom with BIR, sizeable study/guest bedroom, striking bathroom, European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, 2 secure car spaces (1 with overhead storage unit), resident access to a gorgeous BBQ entertainment area with herb garden, onsite gym plus access to the renowned RekDek with gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
Positioned in the Yarra’s Edge precinct, you’re seconds to DFO shopping, Crown Entertainment Complex, city attractions, Spencer Street trams, and Southern Cross Station. You also have a variety of restaurants on South Wharf promenade including Gasolina, West Village NYC, Meat Market, Common Man, and Melbourne Public.
Completing the ultimate lifestyle package is an opportunity to secure a Yarra River located Marina Berth for just $60,000 with a Lease Hold until 1st December 2030.

Description:
Your Tower Two Penthouse - Ready and Waiting
The perfect blend of space and style matched by stunning marina views and a location in the Yarra’s Edge precinct, this tantalising two bedroom, two bathroom apartment promises a Docklands lifestyle to savour.
The northerly views are one of the first things you’ll notice when stepping inside this 20th floor retreat. The tranquil marina and further out to the Docklands are all within your sight and best enjoyed out on the generous undercover balcony, which is easily accessed via the spacious lounge and dining zone.
Whether preparing breakfast, lunch, or dinner, the stone kitchen never fails to impress with a moveable island bench and Smeg stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom boasts its own private balcony along with a walk-in robe and ensuite, meanwhile the other bedroom features a BIR and has access to the main balcony.
Other features include the central bathroom with European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna. Walk to South Wharf Promenade with restaurants and bars including Meat Market, The Boatbuilders Yard, The General Assembly, and Plus 5 Bar. You’re also close to DFO shopping, Crown Entertainment Complex, and public transport including Southern Cross Station.

Seriously Stylish with Sweeping City Views
The ultimate in waterfront style and showcasing tranquil scenes of NewQuay Marina and Melbourne's city lights, this three-bedroom, three-bathroom Quays abode is the ultimate statement in luxury inner-city living.
Enjoying an incredible views, stylish timber floors, quality finishes and with bright full windows, this is a rare opportunity to secure a three bedroom apartment. All 3 bedrooms with their own private ensuites, all with BIRs.
Dedicated lounge and dining zones make for great casual living spaces, while the designer stone kitchen offers a breakfast bar, integrated fridge and SS appliances. Enjoy Quays unrivalled facilities including an indoor pool, spa, gym, tennis court, yoga centre, cinema, and rooftop garden, so near to trams, CBD and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
The Ultimate Penthouse Entertainer
With an unprecedented amount of unique atrium space measuring 69sqm (approx.) and boasting exceptional harbour, city and bay views this stunning two bedroom, two bathroom Penthouse apartment in the new ‘Gold Tower’ of the Aqui/Promenade development defines excitement, sophisticated style and class.
We need to start with the amazing atrium alfresco area which has stunning high ceilings and windows and a superb indoor/outdoor feel. This incredibly distinctive zone is very rare to find in any Docklands building and allows for multiple spaces for meals, drinks and general relaxing as well as unprecedented views of Victoria Harbour. What a great space for pets or children!
Inside, you’ll love the spacious and open lounge and dining zone with sleek wooden floors, while the stone kitchen impresses with an island bench, black tapware, and stainless steel Miele appliances. Both bedrooms come with BIRs including the master bedroom which has an ensuite. Further enjoy a stylish bathroom with a European laundry, reverse cycle heating /cooling, secure intercom, 2 secure car spaces and a storage cage.
Also access a 25m indoor pool, spa, sauna, gym, library, private meeting rooms, lush rooftop garden, and secure on-site bicycle storage as part of the building. Near District Docklands Centre, waterside restaurants, grocery stores, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and the 30, 75, and 86 trams.

Description:
Concavo: the Definition of Waterfront Living
Being one of Lend Lease’s showcase developments, Convesso Concavo is located on the prime water frontage in the best part of Docklands. Inspired by the reflections of light on water and designed to maximise the expansive views over Victoria Harbour and its marina, the bay and fantastic city skyline, the residences have been enjoying a high quality finish, genuine luxury lifestyle as well as embedded sustainable feature throughout.
Apartment 2002 is sitting on the North, West and South corner of 20th floor of the high rise part and the 270 degree views take in almost all the best part of Melbourne including the city skyline, marina and the stunning harbour.
With an approximately 147 sqm of total size, the luxury apartment comprises extensive open plan living, Gourmet Euro kitchen, fully equipped with Miele appliances, massive island bench, main with WIRs and ensuite with bathtub, central bathroom, further two double bedrooms, Euro laundry, great open balcony right on the water side.
Also features, floor to ceiling window all around, central air-conditioning, intercom system and double security car parks and one storage cage.
Convesso Concavo also features 24 hour concierge, indoor pool, spa facilities, private cinema, residents and business lounge.
As an emerging precinct with high population growth and situated in the heart of Docklands, Victoria Harbour is at the west end of Collins St and well within the free tram zone, with walking distance to trains, supermarkets, eateries, banks, a short ride to the elite schools such as Melbourne Grammar, Wesley College as well as Melbourne Uni and RMIT, and all the other great amenities Melbourne can offer. And the unique location surrounded by water, boats and parks, is offering all the residents a truly relaxing, resort style and luxury living!
A great opportunity you will never want to miss out, call us now for your exclusive inspection.
Inspection Strictly by Appointment

Description:
Magnificent Space and Gorgeous Harbour Views 
Situated right on the banks of the serene Victoria Harbour and offering beautiful views of the water, Etihad Stadium, and parts of the CBD to the east, this immaculate and spacious two bedroom apartment is a north-facing treasure you cannot miss. In the sought after Dock 5 complex and seconds to great promenade restaurants, Bourke Street eateries, Buluk Park, Woolworths and local trams.
Accommodation: Every window of this exceptional 11th floor apartment faces Victoria Harbour giving you stunning views no matter where you are, with the undercover balcony also promising an outlook to the east including partial city vistas. With 123 sqm (approx..) of space, take advantage of living highlights that include an extra-large central zone with room for both lounge and dining areas, stone kitchen with full Smeg appliances including a microwave and integrated dishwasher, master bedroom with its own balcony plus ample built-in robes and a double vanity ensuite, 2nd bedroom with BIR, and a stylish bathroom with concealed laundry.
Features: Secure car space, refrigerated wine cellar, ducted heating and cooling, intercom entry, and access to heated swimming pool, gymnasium, and communal BBQ area.

Description:
Water Views at Waterview Walk!
The name says it all, this luxurious property situated on Waterview Walk comes with magnificent harbour views. Live in luxury and comfort on the 16th level of a superb building with access to all the best that inner city living provides.
Located close to transport (Trams and Southern Cross Station), sporting facilities (tennis courts, parks, Etihad Stadium) and cafes in one of Dockland's most popular and established areas.
Overlooking the water and park land, this two bedroom apartment offers the main bedroom with a walk in robe and En-suite and a second bedroom with BIRs and access to a central bathroom with laundry facilities. A spacious kitchen leads into a large lounge and dining area with doors leading to a wide balcony.
This property is a fantastic opportunity for investors and owner occupiers alike. True inner city lifestyle in a growth area, call to enquire today, do not miss out!

Description:
An Exclusive Experience Of Panoramic Perfection
Perched on the 21st floor of the exclusive Tower 5 complex, this luxurious apartment is sheer Docklands bliss that needs to be seen to be believed.
An astonishing amount of natural light, bright floor-to-ceiling windows and premium fittings are just the tip of the iceberg for this inspiring property located in the popular Yarra’s Edge. It’s hard to go past the awe-inspiring vistas found throughout the apartment, with the undercover balcony the ultimate spot to enjoy Northerly views of the city, Yarra River and Docklands.
Spanning approximately 204 square metres plus terrace, the bright interior offers a generous living and dining zone adjoining the premium kitchen with island bench and stainless steel Miele appliances. The master bedroom promises the ultimate in luxury and includes a wall of BIR’s and gorgeous double vanity ensuite with bath. The 3 further bedrooms capture awe-inspiring Port Philip Bay vistas with the flexibility of bedroom 4 to be utilised as an additional living area, all surrounding a central glistening bathroom.
The resplendent internal ambiance is enhanced by ducted heating and cooling, separate laundry, powder room, video intercom, 2 car spaces and two storage cages.
On top of all these amazing extras, you get to enjoy the fantastic Yarra’s Edge precinct which is one of the most sought-after areas in the Docklands. You’re close to the South Wharf Promenade which has bars and eateries such as Plus 5 Bar, Munich Brauhaus, Citizen Café and Bar, and Common Man, while you’re also near the Melbourne Exhibition Centre, DFO shopping, Crown Casino, Etihad Stadium, Polly Woodside, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
